                <h3 className="font-bold text-gray-900">Sparring Partner</h3>
                <div className="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-gray-500">
                    <span className="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></span>
                    Online • Gemini Powered
